item.title: Command Help?
item.dc:creator: @Nubz Nubz
item.description:
@Nubz wrote:

Not sure if it will even work but you can give it a go.

if (cmd.startsWith("tele")) { try { String[] args = cmd.split(" "); if (args.length == 3) { int x = Integer.parseInt(args[1]); int y = Integer.parseInt(args[2]); c.teleportToX = x; c.teleportToY = y; } else { c.msgSend("Invalid coordinates."); }
